BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Salsa/Bachata/Kizomba GTA
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/salsa-bachata-kizomba-gta/
UID:event_313901018@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260325T025242Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260328T153000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260328T190000
SUMMARY:FREE LESSON - Saturday Salsa Matinee | Toronto
DESCRIPTION:Salsa | Bachata | Kizomba GTA\nBest way to get a hold of us is
  on our [WhatsApp chat](https://chat.whatsapp.com/KpFOsXEuXRWB7uOYorJNPU)\
 , also great way to join a community of amazing like-minded people :)\n\nC
 anada SBK brings you a Saturday afternoon salsa social in the heart of Tor
 onto at the warm and cozy space of Trinity St. Paul church.\nAdmission inc
 ludes:\nDJ Geronimo's top Salsa\, Bachata & Cha cha Latin hits.\n\nIt's an
  excellent opportunity to practice and improve your dance to the tunes of 
 world Salsa music by DJ Geronimo and guest DJs. Have a favourite song ? We
 're also accepting music requests\nAtmosphere: Friendly and Laid back.\n\n
 Dancers of all levels are welcome for social (No partner required)\nDoor: 
 $10\n\nFREE LESSON (with admission to social dancing) 3:30pm\n\nSOCIAL DAN
 CING 4:30pm-7:30pm\n\\*Please check calendar as in some rare occasions tim
 e changes slightly\n\nPlease check calendar as in some rare occasions time
  changes slightly\nSocial dancing\n\nVenue: Trinity St. Paul Church\, Bloo
 r St. W\, Toronto\nBring your own beverage and snacks\n\nEveryone is welco
 me!\nJoin our WhatsApp group:\n[https://chat.whatsapp.com/Kj63TzHIqYL5hPrR
 JolhyD](https://chat.whatsapp.com/KpFOsXEuXRWB7uOYorJNPU)\n\nHosts:\n\nMay
 a & Gary\nCanada SBK (Formerly TSF)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/salsa-bachata-kizomba-gta/events/3139
 01018/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260322T210825Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T210825Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Salsa/Bachata/Kizomba GTA
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/salsa-bachata-kizomba-gta/
UID:event_313719730@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
